data.description: Must see! This super clean, turnkey home boasts 2,925 square feet, 4 bedrooms, 3 baths, and a 3-car tandem garage in a cul-de-sac. It is centrally located in a well-kept, quiet neighborhood. The home has natural lighting throughout. You will love the A/C for the warm summer months. There is a large walk-in pantry in the kitchen. The laundry room is conveniently located upstairs by the bedrooms. This home has the always sought after walkout basement. Close to Fort Carson, Peterson AFB, Schriever AFB, and the Colorado Springs Airport. There is easy access to the Powers Corridor which offers a wide variety of restaurants, shopping, movie theaters, and many other entertainment options. Be sure to schedule your showing and check this beauty out soon!
